sub_title: Social Media Strategist & Digital Marketing Specialist, Copywriter, Creative writer, Travel Blogger, Content Creator, Storyteller from Croatia
summary:
My name is Valentina and I am a travel blogger, copywriter & social media manager with some skills in web/graphic designing, development, video editing, and photography. I help people and small companies to grow their businesses and build their brands, and website and establish organic growth.

I also write articles and create content for health, culture, food portals, and companies.

Besides working, I fully enjoy life. I have a passion for travelling, constantly creating, and learning. I believe in ideas and humanity.
I love to enjoy the moment and create unforgettable memories, making connections everywhere I go and everywhere I leave. 

I am a pretty fast learner, a reliable and organized person with analytical and problem-solving skills. My spirit is curious and always hungry for new projects and ideas to accomplish. 

Let’s talk about your needs and inquiries and see how can I help you!

Email me at kookylovestotravel@gmail.com
